COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 1130, L.D. 1695
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment replaces the bill and changes the title. The amendment requires law
33 enforcement agencies to adopt written policies regarding procedures to deal with persons
44 who are believed to be experiencing commercial sexual exploitation or sex trafficking.
